          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-376610b81b135021",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "What is the required minimum balance for a BMO Premium Chequing Account?\nThere\u2019s no minimum balance required with a BMO Premium Chequing Account. If you keep and maintain at least $6,000 in the account, we\u2019ll waive the monthly account fee. Plus, you\u2019ll be eligible for an additional $500 * welcome bonus for opening this account.\nHow many transactions per month do I get with a BMO Premium Chequing Account? With the BMO B M O Premium Chequing Account, you get unlimited transactions *52 per month. When you move money out of your account \u2013 like an ATM A T M withdrawal, bill payment or pre-authorized payment \u2013 that counts as a transaction. Money coming into your account \u2013 like payroll direct deposits or cash deposits at an ATM A T M \u2013 don\u2019t count as transactions.",
